        "Dear Director,",
        "I am writing to inform you that I have lost my student identification card while I was returning to the hostel from hometown and request a replacement of an ID card.",
        "I am facing many issues without an ID card.First and foremost, I am unable to enter college campus.I need to make a manual entry each day at the entrance to get into the college.I cannot attend classes and having trouble with issuing books from the library.Entry is not allowed in the Computer Lab without an ID card.As a result,my study is getting impacted.Also,  I am not allowed to appear for exams approaching next week,  which will have greater impact on the grades. In addition to this, I cannot avail facilities such as gym, swimming pool, transportation etc.",
